    <h1>Release - OCT 2017</h1>
    <h2>Work</h2>
    <h3>DaySheet</h3>
    <hr />
    <h4>Overview</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Extra space at the top of the page has been removed.</li>
        <li>No Show checkbox has been changed to a toggle button.</li>
        <li>Open Case Folder and No Show buttons have been moved above the task list.</li>
        <li>
            A new Task Details section has been added to each case.
            This section displays the details of the selected task in the list.
            The Task list is now selectable by clicking anywhere on the row.
            The Task Details is not automatically displayed when a task is selected.
            This is to keep the focus on the Live Chat during the assessment day.
        </li>
        <li>
            The Invoice Notes have been moved to a tab as well. A count on the tab will indicate if a note exists.
        </li>
        <li>
            The "Wrench" icon is for the Task Tools.
            Each task can have Tools that are system features intended to help complete the task.
            Currently only the Submit Invoice task has tools but we can explore building more in the future.
            Click the Wrench will select the task and activate the Task Details tab where the tool is embedded. Selecting the task by clicking the row does not change the active tab.
        </li>
        <li>Task list action buttons have been replaced with the Task Details tab.</li>
        <li>The task list is now sorted by Due Date and the due date is displayed beside the Task name.</li>
    </ul>
