    <h2>Case Details</h2>
    <h3>Overview</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Reduced the wasted space at the top of the page with a new menu bar (no more Actions button).</li>
        <li>Create new tasks with the New Task Form.</li>
        <li>The New Tasks can be linked with a built in task type or ad-hoc. Built In task types are part of default workflows and can potentially have tools!</li>
        <li>Managing invoices can be done from this page as well. Using the search bar at the top, a user can go directly to the details page and manage invoices from there.</li>
        <li>The Assessment Day and Submit Report tasks are special in that they also update the Appointment Date and Due Date of the case itself. This will keep those dates and the task dates in sync.</li>
        <li>The Assessment Day task opens a Reschedule form to allow them to select from the physicians availability. The Reschedule button at the top is the original form that includes the location if that needs to be changed.</li>
        <li>Note that the tab layout was not applied here with the live chat and comments but it could be in the future.</li>
        <li>FUTURE: Make the Box Integration section of this page a Task Tool for Create Case Folder and Sync and Close Case and Unsync</li>
        <li>FUTURE: Make the Calendar Integration section of this page a Task Tool for Create Calendar Event</li>
    </ul>
